{"tid":988380,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[不定時更新]馬丁童話合集","createTime":"2019-01-20T04:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T21:49:16.000Z","uid":64601,"like":46,"dislike":104,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"86edc12243e55b7ba5d39509cf5e6ff5bc9c43f6","tid":988380,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:27:43.000Z","msg":"從前有三隻小豬，最大嗰隻叫豬大佬，第二大嗰隻叫豬二佬，最細嗰隻叫肥成。 咁呢佢三個有日就要去酒樓食嘢啦，點知做完先知三個都唔記得帶銀包。 肥成就同經理講：對唔住，我哋今日冇帶錢嚟食嘢呀。咁經理好嬲，話：一係我報驚，一係就錢債肉償！<br />\n<br />\n咁佢哋最後就決定錢債肉償。<br />\n<br />\n就變成三隻燒豬的故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e23401ec3fea0a37313a1cf74302c08b4f58f2","tid":988380,"uid":4402,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:28:04.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"1214c18fd95caec4c9b2941909cc3edde31aa209","tid":988380,"uid":64601,"like":147,"dislike":2,"score":145,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:28:05.000Z","msg":"幽默感真係唔可以勉強<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad8571236527672d65e858e1a67db4d6d9dbfc5","tid":988380,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c43e732600838a8f5932267a4609e7e6c9317e","tid":988380,"uid":101898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc0044190e42adf3321cfdc54c8ea12c09382c3","tid":988380,"uid":106426,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:29:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3ea58f9e9eb9914b9f51e373355492473555973","tid":988380,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:30:14.000Z","msg":"-100000/10"},{"pid":"f368c5bc810fdf867c16c3532515ab8f930b142b"